Manon Bresch (a mụrụ na 4 Jenụwarị 1998) bụ onye France-Cameroonian na-eme ihe nkiri.

Bresch gara ụlọ akwụkwọ ihe nkiri Cours Florent na Paris ruo afọ iri na abụọ. O nwere ndị nna nna Cameroon ma gaa ebe ahụ ezumike. Bresch mere ihe nkiri izizi ya n'afọ 2012, na obere ọrụ na Les Papas du dimanche

Bresch malitere igwu Yasmine, ezigbo enyi Salomé, na usoro TV Clem n'afọ 2015. N'ọnwa Septemba afọ 2015, a họpụtara Bresch dịka Thérèse Marci, nwa nwanyị nkuchi nke Thomas na Gabriel, na ihe nkiri ncha Plus belle la vie

Onye na-eme ihe nkiri nke na-emebu ihe nkiri ahụ, Tia Diagne, hapụrụ iji chụsoo ohere ndị ọzọ na-eme ya. N'afọ 2017, Bresch mere Charlotte Castillon, nwa okorobịa na-agba ọsọ nke e gburu n'ụzọ a na-apụghị ịkọwa akọwa n'ihu ọha, na ihe nkiri TV Noir enigma Bresch gosipụtara dịka Luisa, nwa akwụkwọ nwere ikike na voodoo, na 2019 supernatural murder-mystery TV series Mortel. N'afọ 2020, ọ mere Sirley, nwa akwụkwọ na-enye nsogbu si French Guiana, na Maledetta primavera
Na mgbakwunye na French, Bresch na-asụ Bekee na ụfọdụ Spanish
Ọ na-eme judo, tennis, na ịgba egwú nke oge a.
